column5: WE WON!!!!!!! Thanks to your support Yellowknife is getting an animal shelter!!!! Our idea won the top prize in the Aviva Community Fund contest for 2010 and will receive $300,000 to build our shelter.  Thanks to all of you!!!  http://www.avivacomm...org/search/grid
That's absolutely awesome Dave, I heard the news earlier this morning.  Please keep us up to date on the progress.
Congrats!!  Remember spay or neuter your polar bear!
Thats awesome Dave.  Keep us updated  will ya.  Again,congrats.
well that's good, with all the clicking we had to do voting you know how hard we worked getting it done....LOL   glad you won
YAAA BABY !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! GOOD TO KNOW WE CAN ALL AMKE A DIFFERENCE HATS OFF TO EVERYONE!!!
Is it going to have a green roof???? Great news for your community!

is there a start date for construction or is there a bunch of red tape for releasing the money...hopefully you can be there for the grand opening with the first stray to occupy the shelter...  Give yourself a "pat on the back"..you deserve it  Cheers
